snippet.title: JohnSL
snippet.description: Hi, my name is John Socha-Leialoha. I'm a software developer by day, so at home I like to do things more mechanical. That usually means CNC milling, injection molding, or 3D printing (although it sometimes involves electronics as well). I hope you enjoy my channel, where I publish videos on projects that interest me.
